React -- Javascript Library thats used to easily  build web applications.
React is used to create components that function as building blocks. Like LEGOS.

React use a syntax expansion of javascript called - JSX -- Javascript XML.

To create react app -- Use npm create vite@latest
For running the app -- cd my-react-app , npm install , npm run dev.
For restarting the server --- cd enter the app in terminal and then npm run dev.
 